                ))}
              </div>
            </section>
          </>
        ) : (
          /* Community Page Content */
          <div className="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-700">
            {/* Community Hero */}
            <section className="relative overflow-hidden hero-gradient pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-20 md:pb-32">
              <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
                <div className="inline-block py-1 px-4 mb-6 rounded-full bg-[#7FB5B5]/10 border border-[#7FB5B5]/20">
                  <span className="text-[#7FB5B5] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[10px]">
                    Student Network
                  </span>
                </div>
                <h1 className="text-4xl md:text-7xl mb-8 leading-tight font-playfair font-bold">
                  A community built on <br className="hidden md:block" />
                  <span className="italic font-normal text-[#C5A059]">shared inquiry</span> and peer learning.
                </h1>
                <p className="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed font-light">
                  A collaborative academic space where students engage beyond live sessions—through discussion, study circles, and ongoing dialogue led by peers from leading institutions.
                </p>
                <button onClick={() => setModalType('auth')} className="bg-[#1A2238] text-white px-12 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase hover:scale-105 transition shadow-xl active:scale-95">
                  Become Part of the Network
                </button>
              </div>
              <div className="absolute top-20 -left-20 w-64 h-64 bg-[#7FB5B5]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
              <div className="absolute bottom-20 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-[#C5A059]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
            </section>

            {/* Community Sections */}
            <section className="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
              <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div className="space-y-32">
                  {/* Section 1: What the Community Is */}
                  <div className="max-w-3xl">
                    <h2 className="text-3xl font-playfair font-bold mb-8 text-[#1A2238]">What the Community Is</h2>
                    <p className="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
                      The Lumina Community functions as an extension of our platform’s core peer-led philosophy. It is a space centered on thoughtful discussion, collaborative learning, and mutual support among students who prioritize academic depth and clarity. This is not a forum for passive consumption or superficial noise; it is a dedicated network for meaningful exchange, where rigor and intellectual curiosity are the primary standards of entry.
