                        <h4 className="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-[#1A2238]">Concept Clarity Groups</h4>
                        <p className="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Peer-to-peer pods focused on doubt resolution and real-time clarity, ensuring no conceptual hurdle remains unaddressed.</p>
                      </div>
                      <div className="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[#FDFBF7] border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02]">
                        <div className="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059]/10 transition-colors">
                          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C5A059" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 className="font-bold text-xl mb-4 text-[#1A2238]">Reading Groups</h4>
                        <p className="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Scholarly circles dedicated to the critical analysis of foundational texts and contemporary academic research through active conversation.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  {/* Section 3: Who It’s For */}
                  <div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                    <div>
                      <h2 className="text-3xl font-playfair font-bold mb-6 text-[#1A2238]">Who It’s For</h2>
                      <p className="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
                        Lumina is designed for curious students who seek rigorous learning from their peers. It is a network for those who ask questions without hesitation and engage with others who take their academic pursuits seriously. Our participants range from high-performing scholars at top-tier global institutions to motivated independent learners seeking clarity and intellectual community.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div className="bg-[#1A2238] p-10 rounded-[2rem] text-white shadow-2xl scale-100 hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-500">
                      <p className="text-gray-400 italic font-light leading-relaxed">
                        "The community bridges the gap between passive viewing and active understanding. It's where the most profound breakthroughs happen—in the follow-up question, the shared resource, and the collective inquiry."
